  "description": "<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t(1)当句子中有be动词或情态动词时，则把be动词或情态动词(can,could等等)提到主语的前面变成疑问句;</div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; 在be动词或情态动词后面加not变成否定句.</div>\n<div>\n\t例：①陈述句：She is a student.</div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 疑问句&rarr; Is she a student?</div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 否定句&rarr; She is not a student.</div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;②陈述句：I can swim.</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 疑问句&rarr; Can you swim .</div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;否定句&rarr; I can not swim.</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t(2) 当句子中即没有be动词，也没有情态动词时，则在主语前加助动词do (you,以及复数), does(单数she,he,it)变成问句;</div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;在主语后谓语动词前加助动词don&rsquo;t(I,you,以及复数), doesn&rsquo;t(单数she,he,it)变成否定句，助动词后的动词要变成动词原形。</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t例：①陈述句：We get up at 7:00 every morning.</div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 疑问句&rarr;Do you get up at 7:00 every morning?</div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 否定句&rarr;We don&rsquo;t get up at 7:00 every morning.</div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;②陈述句：She has a little brother.</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;疑问句&rarr; Does she have a little brother?</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;否定句&rarr; She doesn&rsquo;t have a little brother</div>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p774679/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p774679\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p772925/\">囧研究：科学告诉你，败钱真的能买开心</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p774392/\">上海迪士尼菜单曝光：当米奇遇上中国菜</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p774489/\">《人物》2016全球最美女人：詹妮弗安妮斯顿</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p769484/\">只有经历这11种情感体验 人生才算完整</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p774528/\">英国女王90大寿：珍贵皇室组照首次发布</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p774561/\">专四必看系列：考前作文密押（十）</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p773830/\">生活达人告诉你：橡皮筋的各种妙用</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p773717/\">你月薪多少？这个答案该告诉你的家人吗</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p773396/\">音标很难记？其实1/3的内容你天生就会</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p774330/\">2016年英语专四考前小tips</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
