  "description": "<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">一般现在时：表示经常性的事情，经常性的动作或一般性事实。</span></div>\n<div>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">时间状语：often 经常，usually通常，always 总是，every每个， sometimes 有时，at &hellip;在几点钟</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span style=\"color: #f00;\">只有在第三人称单数用动词的&ldquo;三单变化&rdquo;，其他用动词的原形。</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t1. she/ he /it + 动词S/ES,</div>\n<div>\n\t2.We/ they/ I/ you+动词原形</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t三单变化：</div>\n<div>\n\t1.多数在动词后+s</div>\n<div>\n\tplay &mdash; plays &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;like &mdash; likes &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">ask---asks &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;work---works &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;get---gets &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;stay---stays </span></div>\n<div>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">(2)以字母s, x, ch, sh或o结尾的动词，在词尾直接加-es. </span></div>\n<div>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">watch---watches &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; wish---wishes &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; fix---fixes &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; do---does &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; go---goes &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; pass---passes</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t(3)以&ldquo;辅音字母加 - y&rdquo;结尾的动词，要先变y为i再加-es.</div>\n<div>\n\ttry---tries &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; study---studies &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; cry---cries &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;fly---flies</div>\n<div>\n\t(4) .不规则变化：</div>\n<div>\n\t<span style=\"color: #f00;\">be---- is are &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; have----has</span></div>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p774677/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p774677\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p772925/\">囧研究：科学告诉你，败钱真的能买开心</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p774392/\">上海迪士尼菜单曝光：当米奇遇上中国菜</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p774489/\">《人物》2016全球最美女人：詹妮弗安妮斯顿</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p769484/\">只有经历这11种情感体验 人生才算完整</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p774528/\">英国女王90大寿：珍贵皇室组照首次发布</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p774561/\">专四必看系列：考前作文密押（十）</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p773830/\">生活达人告诉你：橡皮筋的各种妙用</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p773717/\">你月薪多少？这个答案该告诉你的家人吗</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p773396/\">音标很难记？其实1/3的内容你天生就会</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p774330/\">2016年英语专四考前小tips</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
